#LinearRegression #Train model

lm_goog <- lm(adj ~ . , data = training_goog)

lm_amzn <- lm(adj ~ . , data = training_amzn)

lm_nflx <- lm(adj ~ . , data = training_nflx)

lm_tsla <- lm(adj ~ . , data = training_tsla)

                       number = 10 ,
                       repeats = 3,
